### About this FIle:
This file contains a detailed, ball-by-ball breakdown of IPL matches, compiled and organized from Cricsheet data. It includes essential match details such as team line-ups, batting and bowling performances, wickets, extras, and match outcomes. The dataset also features cumulative statistics for players and teams, making it an extensive resource for cricket analysis. With over 60 attributes, the dataset provides a comprehensive view of each match's dynamics, allowing for in-depth analysis of strategies and player performance across multiple seasons of the IPL.
